307
00:15:29,840 --> 00:15:31,920
That should knock out most any infection.

308
00:15:34,230 --> 00:15:36,270
And oxycontin.

309
00:15:36,270 --> 00:15:38,500
The oxy. We need painkillers.

310
00:15:48,100 --> 00:15:49,760
You want to see the General or not?

311
00:15:51,030 --> 00:15:52,820
This is the last of our supply.

312
00:15:57,730 --> 00:15:58,620
That'll do.

313
00:16:16,550 --> 00:16:18,300
The General will see you now.

314
00:16:19,040 --> 00:16:20,660
