318
00:16:27,030 --> 00:16:28,400
Is sweet Jesus with them?

319
00:16:28,610 --> 00:16:29,610
No, sir.

320
00:16:29,610 --> 00:16:30,740
- Then tell them to go to hell! - I don't believe so.

321
00:16:30,740 --> 00:16:33,370
I've got a war to fight! Where's that close air support I ordered?

322
00:16:33,370 --> 00:16:36,610
Tell the Admiral I need those subs in position by 0800.

323
00:16:36,610 --> 00:16:39,200
Bravo Company, hold your position at all costs.

324
00:16:39,200 --> 00:16:41,170
Repeat, all costs.

325
00:16:41,740 --> 00:16:42,980
You heard the General.

326
00:16:43,430 --> 00:16:44,740
General McCandles, sir.

327
00:16:45,070 --> 00:16:47,140
We're on a mission of extreme importance

328
00:16:47,470 --> 00:16:49,160
by direct order from the president.

329
00:16:50,460 --> 00:16:51,750
It's imperative that we find air transport

330
00:16:51,900 --> 00:16:53,680
-to Mt. Wilson CDC lab - Sorry, I'm busy.

331
00:16:53,890 --> 00:16:54,290
in California.

332
00:16:54,380 --> 00:16:55,900
Where are my reinforcements?

333
00:16:55,900 --> 00:16:57,450
You heard the man. Time to go.

334
00:16:57,450 --> 00:16:58,620
That's it?

335
00:17:00,020 --> 00:17:02,760
I've a good mind to make you barf up my oxycontin.

336
00:17:02,760 --> 00:17:03,570
Doc! Doc! Stand down!

337
00:17:03,570 --> 00:17:05,930
