340
00:17:11,470 --> 00:17:14,040
I have a wounded man in need of medical attention.

341
00:17:16,140 --> 00:17:18,810
Just the doctor. The rest of you wait here.

342
00:17:20,990 --> 00:17:21,810
I got this.

343
00:17:22,510 --> 00:17:23,190
All right.

344
00:17:23,240 --> 00:17:26,070
Hey, hey, hey. Talk to him about the chopper.

345
00:17:41,100 --> 00:17:42,620
Son of a bitch.

346
00:17:42,980 --> 00:17:44,250
I was saving that oxy

347
00:17:44,250 --> 00:17:46,220
for a party when we got to Cali.

348
00:17:52,840 --> 00:17:53,680
You the medic?

349
00:17:53,980 --> 00:17:55,110
I am indeed.

350
00:17:56,060 --> 00:17:57,100
You the General?

351
00:17:57,100 --> 00:17:58,490
General Arthur C. McCandles.

352
00:17:58,540 --> 00:18:00,110
Commander, Central Command,

353
00:18:00,110 --> 00:18:01,870
Infection Response Forces.

354
00:18:09,380 --> 00:18:10,740
Where's your wounded man?

355
00:18:13,020 --> 00:18:13,840
Right here.

356
00:18:23,400 --> 00:18:24,620
It's not a bite.

