358
00:18:28,490 --> 00:18:29,590
Real bad.

359
00:18:29,790 --> 00:18:31,180
It's just a scratch.

360
00:18:32,160 --> 00:18:34,980
No, that's... that's more like gangrene.

361
00:18:36,370 --> 00:18:37,770
Can you save the leg?

362
00:18:38,190 --> 00:18:39,520
I'm afraid not, General.

363
00:18:39,670 --> 00:18:41,260
It's already starting to spread.

364
00:18:41,490 --> 00:18:43,730
Soon the Z virus will take over.

365
00:18:45,100 --> 00:18:46,750
All I can do at this point is show you mercy

366
00:18:46,750 --> 00:18:47,890
when the time comes.

367
00:18:48,820 --> 00:18:50,540
You call that a diagnosis?

368
00:18:51,520 --> 00:18:53,110
I call it the truth.

369
00:18:54,090 --> 00:18:55,230
You're gonna die.

370
00:18:55,430 --> 00:18:56,300
And soon.

371
00:18:56,910 --> 00:18:58,630
