372
00:19:37,950 --> 00:19:39,510
Look who.

373
00:19:40,460 --> 00:19:41,580
What do you think, pup?

374
00:19:41,740 --> 00:19:43,170
Could we use another friend?

375
00:19:45,230 --> 00:19:46,480
My thoughts exactly.

376
00:19:50,820 --> 00:19:52,030
That was quick.

377
00:19:52,300 --> 00:19:54,080
