378
00:19:55,240 --> 00:19:58,020
Awesome. Beautiful Aurora today.

379
00:19:58,030 --> 00:19:59,640
How's your day going?

380
00:19:59,860 --> 00:20:02,460
Kinda lonely. Nice to have somebody to talk to.

381
00:20:03,320 --> 00:20:06,390
I know the feeling. Gets lonely here too.

382
00:20:06,560 --> 00:20:08,600
Keeping an eye on the planet keeps you busy though.

383
00:20:09,110 --> 00:20:10,510
I feel safer just knowing you're there.

384
00:20:10,820 --> 00:20:13,080
You seem so cool.

385
00:20:13,530 --> 00:20:15,130
I wish I could meet you in person.

386
00:20:15,310 --> 00:20:18,970
Super busy, but I'm sure that could be arranged.

387
00:20:20,600 --> 00:20:21,830
What are you doing right now?

388
00:20:25,300 --> 00:20:26,350
Aww you know.

389
00:20:26,760 --> 00:20:28,110
Same ol', same ol'.

390
00:20:34,600 --> 00:20:36,380
One thousand ninety.

391
00:20:37,330 --> 00:20:39,120
One thousand ninety-one.

392
00:20:40,480 --> 00:20:42,260
One thousand and ninety-two.

393
00:20:46,310 --> 00:20:47,720
Okay, what's going on with Doc?

