500
00:27:45,960 --> 00:27:47,500
Obstetrics, huh?

501
00:27:47,610 --> 00:27:49,520
I wonder what that must have been like.

502
00:27:50,660 --> 00:27:53,490
Bringing all them beautiful little angels into the world.

503
00:27:54,790 --> 00:27:58,130
I mean just to be present for so many miracles.

504
00:27:59,710 --> 00:28:03,110
Yeah, it's a bummer all those babies grew up to be zombies.

505
00:28:06,370 --> 00:28:07,280
You know,

506
00:28:07,860 --> 00:28:09,740
I got a kid out there somewhere.

507
00:28:11,820 --> 00:28:13,690
I never told anybody that before.

508
00:28:14,950 --> 00:28:16,430
I had him when I was 19.

509
00:28:17,700 --> 00:28:18,740
Too young.

510
00:28:19,900 --> 00:28:22,210
Wasn't really around for him like I should've been.

511
00:28:22,920 --> 00:28:24,420
Never really got to know him.

512
00:28:26,270 --> 00:28:28,170
Kept telling myself maybe you know

513
00:28:28,830 --> 00:28:32,120
someday I...I would just call him up.

514
00:28:32,870 --> 00:28:34,460
Make up for lost time.

515
00:28:38,030 --> 00:28:40,280
Lost time. Lost time.

516
00:28:42,510 --> 00:28:44,580
And I don't even know if he's alive or dead.

517
00:28:51,920 --> 00:28:53,460
Help!

518
00:28:54,300 --> 00:28:55,920
Help!

519
00:28:56,150 --> 00:28:57,440
Somebody!

520
00:28:57,650 --> 00:28:59,160
Anybody!

521
00:28:59,160 --> 00:29:00,040
Help!

522
00:29:00,040 --> 00:29:02,100
Bravo Company must hold their positions

523
00:29:02,100 --> 00:29:03,680
until the reinforcements arrive.

524
00:29:03,680 --> 00:29:04,750
If their line is broken,

525
00:29:04,750 --> 00:29:06,300
there's nothing to stop the infected

526
00:29:06,300 --> 00:29:07,290
