544
00:30:05,430 --> 00:30:06,500
Murphy!

545
00:30:09,410 --> 00:30:10,560
Murphy!

546
00:30:13,240 --> 00:30:16,160
Murphy! Murphy!

547
00:30:16,900 --> 00:30:17,710
